title: Me and my friend are looking for a ranked team(MemeTeam)
body: Me and my friend Kadius are looking for a ranked team. We like memes and are B1 and S5 though we can assure you were better than our ranks(we don't play much ranked casue more of a casual player than competitive). Were looking for a team that is in around S5 elo and is on a lot(preferably with players over 1000 wins in norms casue it proves experience). We can do any types of comms (Skype, Discord, TeamSpeak etc). My IGN is Xaiveen and my friends is Kadius. Add us if you wanna think about it.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     memez
